# Security, Auth & Rights Layer Visualization

## Authentication Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph "Virtual User System"
        
        subgraph "Registration"
            reg_req["Registration Request"]
            gen_did["Generate DID (Decentralized ID)"]
            gen_keys["Generate Ed25519/X25519 keypair"]
            create_vu["Create VirtualUser record"]
            store_pub["Store public key"]
            return_cred["Return: DID, keypair (secret)"]
        end

        subgraph "Authentication"
            auth_req["Auth Request"]
            sign_challenge["Sign challenge with private key"]
            verify_sig["Verify signature against DID"]
            issue_jwt["Issue JWT access token"]
            issue_refresh["Issue refresh token"]
            create_session["Create server session"]
        end

        subgraph "JWT Claims"
            jwt_sub["sub: did"]
            jwt_iat["iat: issued at"]
            jwt_exp["exp: expiry"]
            jwt_aud["aud: audience (VIVIM)"]
            jwt_role["role: user|admin"]
        end

        subgraph "Token Refresh"
            refresh_req["Refresh token request"]
            validate["Validate refresh token"]
            issue_new["Issue new access token"]
            rotate["Rotate refresh token"]
        end
    end

    reg_req --> gen_did
    gen_did --> gen_keys
    gen_keys --> create_vu
    create_vu --> store_pub
    store_pub --> return_cred

    auth_req --> sign_challenge
    sign_challenge --> verify_sig
    verify_sig --> issue_jwt
    verify_sig --> issue_refresh
    issue_jwt --> create_session

    refresh_req --> validate
    validate --> issue_new
    validate --> rotate
```

