## Zero-Knowledge Privacy

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph "Client-Side Encryption"
        
        client_start["User generates master key"]
        client_derive["Derive encryption key from password"]
        client_key_local["Key NEVER leaves device"]
        
        subgraph "Key Derivation"
            kdf["Argon2 / PBKDF2"]
            salt["Unique salt per user"]
            iter["High iteration count"]
        end
    end

    subgraph "Data Encryption"
        encrypt_data["Encrypt data before sending"]
        alg["Algorithm: XChaCha20-Poly1305"]
        nonce["Unique nonce per message"]
        encrypted["Encrypted payload"]
        send_server["Send to server (cannot read)"]
    end

    subgraph "Decryption"
        receive["Receive encrypted data"]
        derive_key["Re-derive key locally"]
        decrypt["Decrypt with key"]
        verify["Verify integrity"]
        display["Display to user"]
    end

    subgraph "Key Recovery"
        seed["Generate seed phrase (BIP-39)"]
        backup["Backup to cloud (encrypted)"]
        restore["Restore from seed"]
    end

    client_start --> client_derive
    client_derive --> client_key_local
    client_key_local --> encrypt_data
    
    encrypt_data --> alg
    alg --> nonce
    nonce --> encrypted
    encrypted --> send_server
    
    send_server --> receive
    receive --> derive_key
    derive_key --> decrypt
    decrypt --> verify
    verify --> display

    client_key_local --> seed
    seed --> backup
    backup --> restore
```

