## Audit Logging

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API as API Server
    participant Audit as Audit Log
    participant DB as Database

    User->>API: Request (with auth token)
    API->>API: Check permissions
    
    alt Access Granted
        API->>API: Process request
        API->>DB: Execute query
        DB-->>API: Result
        
        Note over API: Log access event
        API->>Audit: write_event({
            user_id,
            action,
            resource,
            resource_id,
            result: "success",
            timestamp,
            ip_address,
            user_agent
        })
        
        API-->>User: Response
    else Access Denied
        Note over API: Log denial event
        API->>Audit: write_event({
            user_id,
            action,
            resource,
            result: "denied",
            reason,
            timestamp,
            ip_address
        })
        
        API-->>User: 403 Forbidden
    end

    Note over User: Query audit trail
    User->>API: GET /audit/events
    API->>Audit: query_events(filters)
    Audit-->>API: Event list
    API-->>User: Paginated audit trail
```

